         </li>
         <li style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Communicating With You</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">. We may use your information to communicate with you, respond to and/or follow-up on your requests, inquiries, issues, or feedback, and to provide you with customer service.</span></p>
         </li>
         <li style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Marketing and Promotional Purposes</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">. We use your information for marketing and promotional purposes, to send marketing, to engage in advertising, and to engage in promotional messages to you via email, text, or postal mail. We may also use your information to show you advertisements for our Products and to administer promotions and other programs.</span></p>
         </li>
         <li style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Analytics and Personalization</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">. We use your information to conduct research and analytics, including to improve our Products, our stores, to understand how you use our Websites, to engage in marketing campaigns, to personalize your experience, to customize our marketing and advertising we show you, and to better understand your needs and the needs of our customers and partners.</span></p>
         </li>
         <li style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Security and Fraud Prevention</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">. We use your information to detect, investigate, prevent, or take action regarding possible malicious, deceptive, fraudulent, or illegal activity, including fraudulent transactions, attempts to violate our policies and terms, security incidents, and harm to the rights, property, or safety of us and our customers, employees, and other stakeholders.</span></p>
         </li>
         <li style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Legal Obligations</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">. We may use your information to comply with our legal and regulatory obligations, establish or protect our legal rights, or defend against a legal claim.</span></p>
