            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">With Your Consent.</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">&nbsp;We may disclose or share your information with your consent, which may be obtained in writing; online, through &ldquo;click-through&rdquo; agreements; when you accept the terms &amp; conditions on our Websites; orally, either in person or on the phone; or by other means.</span></p>
