         </li>
         <li style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">To Affiliated Third Parties.</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">&nbsp;We may disclose your information with certain third parties that are affiliated with us, such as parent and subsidiary companies.</span></p>
         </li>
         <li style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
            <p><strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">To Non-Affiliated Third Parties</span></strong><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">. We may disclose your information to non-affiliated third parties, such as our service providers, to support our core business functions and internal operations, such as fulfilling orders, delivering packages, complying with your request to ship Products, send postal mail, e-mails, and text messages, analyze customer data, provide marketing and advertising, administering the Websites, processing payments, investigating fraud, conducting surveys, and providing customer service.</span></p>
